T1  - Reorganizing the Boundaries of Trust: From Discrete Alternatives to Hybrid Forms
AU  - McEvily, Bill
Y1  - 2011/05/17
PY  - 2011
DA  - 2011/10/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/orsc.1110.0649
DO  - 10.1287/orsc.1110.0649
